# Component naming

Name components from least descriptive (most general) to most specific.

The leftmost part is the broader category; each following part narrows it down.

```ts
// Prefer
ButtonIcon   // Button > Icon
ButtonStar   // Button > Star
SvgStar      // Svg > Star

// Avoid
IconButton   // Icon before Button
StarButton   // Star before Button
StarSvg      // Star before Svg
```

File names follow the same order in kebab-case: `button-icon.tsx`, `button-star.tsx`, `svg-star.tsx`.
